  <mainContent><![CDATA[<h3>Follow these six easy steps to apply for one of our Apprenticeship Pathways.</h3>
<ul>
<li>Decide on the pathway you are interested in from <a data-udi="umb://document/a698ad2c73fe40968602592bf5e55949" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a698ad2c73fe40968602592bf5e55949}" title="Our Apprenticeships">our courses</a></li>
<li>Complete our quick and straightforward <a href="https://www.uspcollege.ac.uk/courses-apprenticeships/apply/create-an-account/" title="Apply">online application form</a> </li>
<li>You will then be invited to the college for an interview so we can find out more about you</li>
<li>Dependent on your grades in English, Maths and ICT you may have to attend an assessment appointment – usually around 2 hours</li>
<li>We will work together with you to help find an employer</li>
<li>You will have an interview with your potential employer – don’t worry we can help with interview techniques</li>
<li>If you are successful, we will enrol your onto your new Apprenticeship!</li>
</ul>]]></mainContent>
